        h2 DETAILED INFORMATION
        div.info 
            h3 WORKING DAYS 
            p Classes are conducted every week from Monday To Saturday
        div.info 
            h3 WORKING TIME
            p Classes are open from Morning 9:00 AM - 7:00PM
            h4 Our Schedule: 
            p 9:00AM - 11:30AM : Hip-Hop
            p 11:30AM - 1:00PM : FreeStyle 
            p 1:00PM - 3:00PM : Lunch Time
            p 3:00PM - 5:00PM : Classical 
            p 5:00PM - 7:00PM : Jazz
    section.Contact-me
        h2 Get In Touch 
        div.links 
            img(src="/static/Image/gmail.png" alt="Gmail")
            img(src="/static/Image/instagram.png" alt="Instagram")
            img(src="/static/Image/linkedin.png" alt="Linkedin") 